Definition:Auchenoceros punctatus ; ...Ahuruhuru; Red mullet; <i> Upeneichthys lineatus</i> [reference 1982 Ayling and Cox] -->pink cod, a sea fish. W.4 A[a]huru (ii), a[a]huruhuru  n. <i> Auchenoceros punctatus </i>, a sea fish, scaleless, about size of  raawaru.] <i> Auchenoceros punctatus </i>  See pink cod.
